  "favicon": "https://toucharcade.com/styles/toucharcade/toucharcade/favicon/favicon-196x196.png",
  "text": "Hey TouchArcade, Michael here from WHALEO announcing a new voice-narrated puzzle game: The Valley of the Architects. Beta is currently open via testflight, send your testflight info to media @ whaleo.com . Looking forward to your feedback. Description The Valley follows Liz, an architectural writer, across the looming regions of Africa as she tries to uncover the story of the mysterious architect. As she reaches each summit she is presented with puzzles hidden in each monument. Using her skills, she will have to overcome each puzzle. As the story unravels around her it becomes clear that there is nothing quite like a waltz though The Valley... Screenshots (Gameplay trailer coming soon) Thanks so much. Your feedback is a HUGE help! Honestly I don’t know if it’s just me but I didn’t make it very far, I found the visuals looked great but it also made it difficult for me to properly see everything clearly so I gave up. Not sure yet hoping for end of summer. Need to work out the kinks so nothing official yet! Thanks for playing! When you say difficult to see what in particular? The player? Where to go? Something else? Appreciate the feedback Hey all, Just released an update to the beta. If you want to join you can send me your testflight privately. Looking forward to hearing your feedback! Getting close to the finish line. Lots of new updates made to the game. To try the BETA send me your testflight and I'll add you. Thanks. Hey TA! Been awhile seen the last update. The Valley of the Architects is still on the way. Latest testing is ongoing now in TestFlight. Let me know if you want in! Right now still figuring out the tutorial. Worried it may need to be scrapped and start from ground up. Let me know what you think. Best, Mike Hey TA! First trailer for The Valley of the Architects out now! Final testing happening now. Send me a message if you would like to join the TestFlight. Also have a Steam playtest happening if you have Steam and would like to try it out. In this update: Achievements More options Revised main menu Revised levels/puzzles Lots of bug fixes Looking forward to hearing from you all! Best, Mike Hey TA! Pre-Order The Valley of the Architects here! Looking for a few testers to iron out some questions. Send me a message if you would like to join the TestFlight. Looking forward to hearing from you all! Best, Mike Hey TA! Quick update for The Valley of the Architects, it's been awhile. Long story short, game was delayed to get the steam version in order. The steam version is more of a separate game with significant changes. You can check it out here. However, I haven't left the iOS version in the background. Here's a list of major upgrades for the iOS version: Update to graphics and level design New mechanics including moving walls and laser switches Revised Puzzles More options/settings (including Ambient Occlusion and Temporal Anti-Aliasing New Music Check out the latest trailer below and PREORDER the game now here. Pricing may change but preorder will lock you in to the cheapest price at launch and will also help boost store presence on launch day so would be a big help! Looking forward to hearing from you all! Best, Mike Share This Page",
